---
layout: default.njk
title: Writing
eleventyImport:
  collections: ["post"]
published: Sept 18, 2024
---

<div>
  <div class="mb-12">
    <h1 class="mb-2">Articles</h1>
    <p class="text-secondary">
      How-to articles on various specific problems I've solved.
    </p>
  </div>

  <ul>
    {%- for post in collections.post | reverse -%}
    <li class="my-6">
      <a
        class="block p-8 border border-solid rounded border-action fancy-hover bg-action-card-hover"
        href="{{ post.url }}"
      >
        {% if post.data.draft %}
        <span
          class="text-xs bg-orange-900 text-white font-bold px-2 py-1 rounded-full inline-block mb-2"
        >
          ðŸš§ Under Construction
        </span>
        {% endif %}
        <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="text-secondary font-light text-sm my-2">
          Last updated: {{post.date | postDate}}
        </p>

        <ul class="flex items-center flex-wrap gap-4">
          {%- for tech in post.data.techStack -%}
          <li class="chip">
            {{ tech.name }} {% if tech.version %}v{{tech.version}}{% endif %}
          </li>
          {%- endfor -%}
        </ul>
      </a>
    </li>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </ul>
</div>
